sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Python SDK
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Training Operator<br/>Watch + Reconcile
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Scheduler as Gang Scheduler<br/>(scheduler-plugins)
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet<br/>10250/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workers as Training Worker Pods<br/>Framework-specific ports
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics scraping

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: PyTorchJob Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate CR<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS<br/>Kubernetes API auth
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated + defaulted
        K8sAPI-->>User: Job created
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Operator,Kubelet: Flow 2: Job Reconciliation
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>PyTorchJob created<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount
        Operator->>Operator: Reconcile job<br/>Calculate replicas
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Scheduler: PodGroup created
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>For pod discovery<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
        Scheduler->>K8sAPI: Gang schedule pods<br/>All or nothing<br/>HTTPS/6443
        K8sAPI->>Kubelet: Schedule pods<br/>HTTPS/10250 TLS1.2+<br/>Node auth
        Kubelet-->>Workers: Start containers<br/>Inject env vars
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Workers: Flow 3: Distributed Training
        Workers->>Workers: Inter-pod communication<br/>PyTorch: torchrun protocol<br/>TensorFlow: gRPC<br/>MPI: MPI protocol<br/>Framework-specific encryption
        Workers->>Workers: Model synchronization<br/>Gradient exchange
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,Operator: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 No encryption<br/>No auth (ClusterIP)
        Operator-->>Prometheus: controller_runtime_*<br/>workqueue_*<br/>rest_client_*
    end

    rect rgb(248, 248, 255)
        Note over Workers,Operator: Flow 5: Job Completion
        Workers->>Workers: Training complete<br/>Exit code 0
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch: Pod status<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update job status<br/>Succeeded/Failed<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Event<br/>HTTPS/6443
        K8sAPI-->>User: Job status available
    end
